OL,7,FThe mother of a teenager who was
OL,8,Fmurdered with a so-called ninja sword
OL,9,Fin Wolverhampton has pleaded with MPs
OL,10,Fto ban the dangerous weapons.
OL,12,FRonan Kanda, 16, was whilst walking to
OL,13,Fa friend's house in in June 2022.
OL,15,FA vote will be held in Parliament on
OL,16,Fthe evening of Wednesday 15 May which
OL,17,Fwould ban the sale of so-called ninja
OL,18,Fswords.
