OL,7,FLabour is calling on all MPs to back
OL,8,Fthe vote, as well as wanting more
OL,9,Feffective and enforced ID checks on
OL,10,Fpeople trying to buy knives online.
OL,12,FIt comes as the Home Secretary
OL,13,Fannounced that the Government will
OL,14,Finvest a further #3.5 million to
OL,15,Ftackle knife crime.
