OL,7,FPooja Kanda told ITV News Central: "I
OL,8,Ffelt sickened by the thought that
OL,9,Fthese things are available to other
OL,10,Fpeople. This could happen, what
OL,11,Fhappened to my child, again. So we as
OL,12,Fa family wanted to do something. We
OL,13,Ffelt the pain of what has happened, I
OL,14,Fdo not want this to happen to anyone
OL,15,Felse".
OL,17,FRonan was stabbed twice with a 'ninja
OL,18,Fsword' on Mount Road, in Lanesfield -
OL,19,Fyards from the front door to his home
OL,20,Fafter he'd been to buy a gaming
OL,21,Fconsole.
