OL,7,FPrabjeet Veadhesa and Sukhman
OL,8,FShergill, both 17, were sentenced to
OL,9,Flife in prison, with a minimum of 18
OL,10,Fyears, for Ronan's murder.
OL,12,FRonan's sister, Nikita, fronted a anti-
OL,13,Fknife crime campaign in November 2023
OL,14,F- urging people to help save a life by
OL,15,Freporting information about anyone
OL,16,Fcarrying a knife.
