OL,7,FThe Government says the new investment
OL,8,Finto knife crime will go into the
OL,9,Fresearch, development and evaluation
OL,10,Fof new technologies which can detect
OL,11,Fknives carried from a distance and
OL,12,Fhand-held or body-worn systems which
OL,13,Fcan be operated by individual officers.
