OL,7,FHome Secretary James Cleverly said:
OL,8,F"Knife crime ruins lives and recent
OL,9,Ftragedies show there's a lot more to
OL,10,Fbe done to take these dangerous
OL,11,Fweapons off our streets. That's why
OL,12,Fwe're taking a joint approach and
OL,13,Fannouncing further measures to tackle
OL,14,Fthese heinous crimes.
OL,16,F"No technology can replace the
OL,17,Fpresence of officers on our streets,
OL,18,Fbut as criminals develop new
OL,19,Fstrategies towards crime, so must we.
